These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, blue, yellow, mauve
House: victorian, colonial, craftsman, tower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, july, june
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, architect, nurse, firefighter
 1. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the colonial house##1
 5. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
 6. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
 8. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
 9. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
10. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the electrician and the person who likes turquise##7
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
13. the firefighter is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color   | mauve    | blue | yellow    | turquise   |
| House   | victorian | craftsman | colonial | tower |
| Birthday           | november       | july   | june  | february     |
| Job     | electrician      | nurse   | firefighter    | architect    |

