 1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 2. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
 3. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the fan techno##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 5. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 6. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fan reggae##5
 7. the fan techno is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the pall-mall-smoker##7
 8. the fan d&b is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan d&b is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
10. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
11. the davidoff-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
