The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, roller, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who likes amber##1
 4. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 5. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 6. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 7. the person who growsbegonia is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person who growsbellflower##6
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
12. the person who likes pink is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
