.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, chinese, colombian, dutch
House: victorian, wooden, cape-cod, ranch-style
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, august, april
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, techno, funk, hip-hop
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the colombian##1
 2. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is between the fan hip-hop and the fan funk##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the victorian house##1
 5. the wooden house is not the fan techno##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
 7. the dutch is somewhere between the nigerian and the ranch-style house##7
 8. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the fan funk##5
 9. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
10. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the nigerian is the cape-cod house##1
12. the cape-cod house is not the fan funk##6

.:: Answer ::.
