.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, white, orange, lavender
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, january, november
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, scrabble, poker
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, bus, snowmobile, bike
 1. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
 2. the person driving the trike is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
 4. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the bus is not the person playing scrabble##6
 7. the person playing scrabble is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 8. the person driving the trike is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 9. the person playing poker is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
10. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person who likes white##6
13. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing poker##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
15. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3

.:: Answer ::.
