.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blood-red, black, brown
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, polish, argentine, nigerian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, may, august, march
City: nizza, prague, san-francisco, rome
 1. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
 2. the argentine is the person who likes black##1
 3. the person traveling to prague is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes blood-red##2
 5. the italian is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the argentine and the person who likes chestnut##7
 7. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is the person traveling to nizza##1
 9. the polish is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
12. the italian is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color   | brown      | black     | blood-red   | chestnut    |
| Nationality     | nigerian | argentine   | polish | italian |
| Birthday     | march        | august     | december  | may      |
| City   | prague       | rome | nizza   | san-francisco    |

 